title: Move to the Music -- Noggin, Laurie Berkner, Dan Zanes, & Jack
description:
The ten famous songs from Move to the Music, originally filler music videos run between Noggin shows, and then a half-hour special which launched the kid-oriented careers of Laurie Berkner, Dan Zanes, and others, as well as prompting the creation of Jack's Big Music Show.
